    "content": {
        "title": "Optimizing the Layout of Nick Name",
        "body": "<ol>\n<li>From the <strong>Project</strong> explorer, expand <strong>frmAddRecipient </strong>&gt;<strong> flxAddRecipient </strong>&gt;<strong> flxEntryFields</strong>, and select <strong>flxNickName</strong>.</li>\n<li>From the <strong>Properties</strong> panel, navigate to the <strong>Look </strong>tab.</li>\n<li>Under the <strong>Flex</strong> section, modify the following values:<br />\n<ul>\n<li>Width: <strong>240 Dp</strong></li>\n<li>Top: <strong>24 Dp</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>"
